**Data quality issues observed**:
- Most auto/category items have empty quickSpecs (no display, processor, etc.)
- Most Wikidata-seeded items have `basePrice: 0` and no real prices
- Many items have `rating: 0` and empty reviews (LLM never processed them)
- Review counts are synthetic: `int(popularity * 12)` (build.py line 86)
- Brand logos rely on external CDN (brandfetch.io, simpleicons.org) -- fragile

